{"tid":1201297,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【引渡惡法】美國務院警告 送中條例危及香港關係法","createTime":"2019-06-11T03:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T03:54:56.000Z","uid":78546,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"42d4734555c22ba693d7f359d41d1f2ca5bdcb19","tid":1201297,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:54:31.000Z","msg":"香港百萬人遊行反對修改逃犯條例，美國周一（10日）回應事件，對於允許疑犯引渡到中國表示嚴重關切，並警告此舉可危及華盛頓對香港提供的特殊地位。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發言人奧特加斯（Morgan Ortagus）周一在定期新聞發布上稱，香港的「一國兩制」持續被侵蝕，威脅到香港國際上長期擁有的特殊地位。<br />\n<br />\n美國國會在1992年通過《香港關係法》法案，承認1997年回歸後香港為獨立關稅區，在一國兩制框架之下，將香港區別於中國，支持香港擁有人權、民主與自治，並保障香港人的生活方式，以及美資在港可自由營商。"},{"pid":"a82d5afb31fa5e02f318b14f0e97b9c8a4fa0ba5","tid":1201297,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:54:56.000Z","msg":"原文<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-hongkong-extradition-usa/u-s-warns-extradition-law-changes-may-jeopardize-hong-kongs-special-status-idUSKCN1TB2EJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-hongkong-extradition-usa%2Fu-s-warns-extradition-law-changes-may-jeopardize-hong-kongs-special-status-idUSKCN1TB2EJ&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVD6jakGblTMbnvy6EODhsvCk%3D&h=a469b655\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-hongkong-extradition-usa%2Fu-s-warns-extradition-law-changes-may-jeopardize-hong-kongs-special-status-idUSKCN1TB2EJ&h=466f2dc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-hongkong-extradition-usa/u-s-warns-extradition-law-changes-may-jeopardize-hong-kongs-special-status-idUSKCN1TB2EJ</a>"}]}